Let's start the minikube cluster we have already configured in the chapter ["Preparing the environment"]({{ page.framework_id | append: "/100_basic/20_cluster.html" | relative_url }}):
```powershell
minikube start
```

Set the default Namespace so that you don't have to specify it every time you invoke `kubectl`:
```powershell
kubectl config set-context minikube --namespace=werf-guide-app
```

