Its lack means that a new minikube cluster was created instead of using the old one. In this case, repeat [all the steps]({{ page.framework_id | append: "/100_basic/20_cluster.html" | relative_url }}) required to install the environment using minikube.

Now run the command in the background PowerShell terminal (do not close its window):
```powershell
minikube tunnel --cleanup=true
```
